i < 6; i++) {\n          var myCanvas = document.createElement(\"canvas\");\n          var myContext = myCanvas.getContext(\"2d\");\n          myCanvas.width = myImage.height;\n          myCanvas.height = myImage.height;\n          myContext.drawImage(\n            myImage,\n            myImage.height * i,\n            0,\n            myImage.height,\n            myImage.height,\n            0,\n            0,\n            myImage.height,\n            myImage.height\n          );\n          // 从Canvas创建贴图\n          mtTexture[i] = new THREE.CanvasTexture(myCanvas);\n        }\n        // 使用 6 幅贴图创建天空盒材质\n        var myMaterials = [];\n        for (var i = 0; i < 6; i++) {\n          var myMaterial = new THREE.MeshBasicMaterial({\n            map: mtTexture[i],\n          });\n          myMaterials.push(myMaterial);\n        }\n        // 使用 6 幅贴图创建天空盒\n        var myMesh = new THREE.Mesh(\n          new THREE.BoxGeometry(1, 1, 1),\n          myMaterials\n        );\n        // 实现 6 幅图像在立方体的里面，而不是在外面\n        myMesh.geometry.scale(1, 1, -1);\n        myScene.add(myMesh);\n      };\n\n      animate();\n\n      function animate() {\n        requestAnimationFrame(animate);\n        myOrbitControls.update();\n        myRenderer.render(myScene, myCamera);\n      }\n    </script>\n  </body>\n</html>\n"
